abstract: Chinese state news media reports rescue of 11 workers trapped in gypsum mine collapse in eastern province of Shandong; 18 other miners have been located but remain trapped.
lead_paragraph: Rescuers pulled 11 workers to safety and located 18 others who were trapped after a mine collapsed in the eastern province of Shandong, state news media said.
